    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReadOnlyPullRequestDto

    public class ScmPullRequestDto
extends TrackerItemDto
    A special tracker item representing a request to pull changes from a source repository/branch and merge them into a target repository/branch. Captures all specialization of pull requests, like e.g. fixed set of status values (PENDING, REVOKED, REJECTED, COMPLETED), fixed custom fields (source repository, target repository, change set IDs, etc.), but reuses all TrackerItemDto functionality. Its getters and setters delegate to the appropriate methods in the parent class.
